# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:13
translate spanish jamie14a_b6dcf387:

    # "As I'm leaving for school, somebody calls my name."
    "Cuando me voy al instituto, alguien me llama por mi nombre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:14
translate spanish jamie14a_b5d0fc44:

    # "Voice" "Hey, [pcname]!"
    "Voice" "¡Eh, [pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:17
translate spanish jamie14a_42b89db9:

    # "Jamie's dad is waving me down and walking towards me."
    "El padre de Jamie me hace señas para que me detenga y camina hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:18
translate spanish jamie14a_8164aaf1:

    # "Wow, he's looking pretty rough. What the hell does he want?"
    "Vaya, tiene muy mal aspecto. ¿Qué coño quiere?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:19
translate spanish jamie14a_cded88c7:

    # "I almost don't even stop. I don't have anything to say to this guy. I want to just keep going to my car and leave."
    "Casi ni me detengo. No tengo nada que decirle a este tipo. Solo quiero seguir hasta mi coche y marcharme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:20
translate spanish jamie14a_aead936c:

    # "But something in his expression and his voice slows me down."
    "Pero algo en su expresión y en su voz me hace frenar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:23
translate spanish jamie14a_bea7ca65:

    # jd "Hey, [pcname], can we talk for a minute?"
    jd "Oye, [pcname], ¿podemos hablar un momento?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:24
translate spanish jamie14a_810a98a2:

    # pc "What do you want?"
    pc "¿Qué quieres?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:25
translate spanish jamie14a_e6116fb2:

    # jd "I want to... apologize."
    jd "Quiero... pedirte perdón."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:26
translate spanish jamie14a_65abe2d1:

    # jd "I messed up."
    jd "La cagué."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:29
translate spanish jamie14a_e9e8048e:

    # jd "I don't like you very much. I'm sure you know that."
    jd "No me caes muy bien. Seguro que lo sabes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:30
translate spanish jamie14a_f70317e8:

    # jd "You broke her heart. I saw how much it hurt her."
    jd "Le rompiste el corazón. Vi lo mucho que le dolió."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:31
translate spanish jamie14a_62f4e049:

    # jd "She stopped going out with her friends. Stopped trusting people."
    jd "Dejó de salir con sus amigos. Dejó de confiar en la gente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:32
translate spanish jamie14a_3e24a9b7:

    # jd "And I hated you for that. For hurting my little girl."
    jd "Y te odié por eso. Por hacerle daño a mi pequeña."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:33
translate spanish jamie14a_3ef77f3d:

    # jd "When she accepted you back so easily, I didn't understand, and I felt like I needed to protect her from you."
    jd "Cuando ella te aceptó de vuelta tan fácilmente, no lo entendí, y sentí que tenía que protegerla de ti."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:36
translate spanish jamie14a_4c6162ef:

    # jd "But now she's been hurt again and this time it wasn't you that did it."
    jd "Pero ahora la han vuelto a hacer daño y esta vez no has sido tú quien lo ha hecho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:37
translate spanish jamie14a_154a6154:

    # jd "It was me."
    jd "He sido yo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:38
translate spanish jamie14a_da05beb6:

    # jd "She really loves you, [pcname]."
    jd "Ella te quiere de verdad, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:39
translate spanish jamie14a_b624fa00:

    # jd "And she's going to resent me forever if I stand in the way of that."
    jd "Y me guardará rencor para siempre si me interpongo en eso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:40
translate spanish jamie14a_ab239c58:

    # pc "So you're saying that I can date Jamie again?"
    pc "¿Entonces estás diciendo que puedo volver a salir con Jamie?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:43
translate spanish jamie14a_7ffe4964:

    # jd "I'm saying that I'm going to step aside and let her do what she wants."
    jd "Estoy diciendo que voy a hacerme a un lado y dejar que ella haga lo que quiera."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:44
translate spanish jamie14a_47573d93:

    # jd "And I'm going to do my best to get along with you."
    jd "Y voy a hacer todo lo posible por llevarme bien contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:45
translate spanish jamie14a_07df80d6:

    # jd "And I hope that you'll accept my apology for getting too protective and overbearing."
    jd "Y espero que aceptes mis disculpas por haber sido demasiado protectora y autoritaria."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:46
translate spanish jamie14a_a1317b53:

    # jd "I just can't stand seeing her sad."
    jd "Es que no soporto verla triste."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:49
translate spanish jamie14a_359770ca:

    # jd "So, I'd like to have you over for dinner tonight, if you're not busy."
    jd "Así que me gustaría invitarte a cenar esta noche, si no estás ocupado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:50
translate spanish jamie14a_ec06b19e:

    # jd "To show Jamie that I'm okay with you two."
    jd "Para demostrarle a Jamie que no tengo ningún problema con vosotros dos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:51
translate spanish jamie14a_bd436701:

    # jd "And to try to repair this whole situation."
    jd "Y para intentar arreglar toda esta situación."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:52
translate spanish jamie14a_19e76fb9:

    # jd "If that's okay with you?"
    jd "¿Te parece bien?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:53
translate spanish jamie14a_35da6d22:

    # pc "Sure, I think I can do that."
    pc "Claro, creo que puedo hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:54
translate spanish jamie14a_aec7f7b0:

    # jd "Will you shake my hand and put all this behind us?"
    jd "¿Me das la mano y dejamos todo esto atrás?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:57
translate spanish jamie14a_a17b9866:

    # pc "Yeah, I think that's a good idea."
    pc "Sí, creo que es una buena idea."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:58
translate spanish jamie14a_501230c4:

    # jd "Good. I'm sorry again."
    jd "Bien. Lo siento de nuevo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:59
translate spanish jamie14a_5487b9f8:

    # jd "I can see you're not the same as you were back then."
    jd "Veo que ya no eres el mismo que eras entonces."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:60
translate spanish jamie14a_3e716201:

    # jd "I've seen how much happier Jamie has been since you've come back to Skyhill."
    jd "He visto lo mucho más feliz que ha estado Jamie desde que volviste a Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:61
translate spanish jamie14a_bb7d1c41:

    # jd "I just want her to be happy."
    jd "Solo quiero que ella sea feliz."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:62
translate spanish jamie14a_78ca39f6:

    # pc "I'll do my best to keep making her happy. I promise."
    pc "Haré todo lo posible por seguir haciéndola feliz. Te lo prometo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:65
translate spanish jamie14a_c390597e:

    # jd "Alright, [pcname]. Well I'll see you later tonight."
    jd "Vale, [pcname]. Bueno, nos vemos esta noche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:66
translate spanish jamie14a_bf178f5a:

    # jd "How do you like your steaks?"
    jd "¿Cómo te gustan los filetes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:67
translate spanish jamie14a_2e9a5edb:

    # pc "Medium rare."
    pc "Poco hechos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:68
translate spanish jamie14a_778e6fc8:

    # jd "Good answer. See, I like you better already."
    jd "Buena respuesta. ¿Ves? Ya me caes mejor."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:69
translate spanish jamie14a_4a59320d:

    # pc "Okay, see you later."
    pc "Vale, hasta luego."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:72
translate spanish jamie14a_0ced9731:

    # "After Jamie's dad leaves, I get in the car and head to school."
    "Cuando se marcha el padre de Jamie, me subo al coche y me dirijo al colegio."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:73
translate spanish jamie14a_1503cf89:

    # "Guess I'm going to be having dinner with them tonight."
    "Supongo que esta noche cenaré con ellos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:74
translate spanish jamie14a_6b9b4f27:

    # "I hope it's not too awkward!"
    "¡Espero que no sea demasiado incómodo!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:76
translate spanish jamie14a_20fd986c:

    # "Later that evening..."
    "Más tarde esa noche..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:86
translate spanish jamie14_e1943713:

    # "I go home and get dressed, putting on something a little nicer than my work clothes, before walking over to Jamie's house to have dinner with her and her dad."
    "Me voy a casa y me cambio, poniéndome algo un poco más elegante que mi ropa de trabajo, antes de ir andando a casa de Jamie para cenar con ella y su padre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:89
translate spanish jamie14_00286863:

    # "Before I even knock, Jamie's dad opens the door and greets me."
    "Antes incluso de llamar a la puerta, el padre de Jamie abre y me saluda."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:90
translate spanish jamie14_05eb9994:

    # jd "Hey, [pcname]. Glad you came."
    jd "Hola, [pcname]. Me alegro de que hayas venido."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:91
translate spanish jamie14_fc7fda3f:

    # jd "I wasn't sure you would. I know this is going to be a little awkward for everybody."
    jd "No estaba seguro de que lo harías. Sé que esto va a ser un poco incómodo para todos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:92
translate spanish jamie14_87d64340:

    # pc "I think it'll be okay."
    pc "Creo que todo irá bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:93
translate spanish jamie14_f9d3ac60:

    # jd "Good. I hope so. Come on in, I just put the steaks on the grill."
    jd "Bien. Eso espero. Pasa, acabo de poner los filetes en la parrilla."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:96
translate spanish jamie14_baa894d7:

    # pc "Where's Jamie?"
    pc "¿Dónde está Jamie?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:97
translate spanish jamie14_a4f2a7fd:

    # jd "She's still up in her room. She's barely left since I made her break up with you."
    jd "Sigue arriba en su habitación. Apenas ha salido desde que la obligué a romper contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:98
translate spanish jamie14_f3737b26:

    # jd "I'm going to call her down for dinner when it's ready and let you surprise her."
    jd "La llamaré para que baje a cenar cuando esté todo listo y dejaré que le des una sorpresa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:101
translate spanish jamie14_473a3bfb:

    # jd "I think it'll make her happy to see us getting along."
    jd "Creo que le hará feliz ver que nos llevamos bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:102
translate spanish jamie14_217a60e1:

    # pc "I hope so. I'm looking forward to seeing her."
    pc "Eso espero. Tengo muchas ganas de verla."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:103
translate spanish jamie14_f8b1bf29:

    # pc "I've been missing her the last week."
    pc "La he echado de menos esta última semana."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:104
translate spanish jamie14_b320763c:

    # jd "Yeah. I know she missed you too. I'm sorry again."
    jd "Sí. Sé que ella también te ha echado de menos. Lo siento de nuevo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:105
translate spanish jamie14_d68d94af:

    # pc "It's alright. I know you were just trying to protect your daughter."
    pc "No pasa nada. Sé que solo intentabas proteger a tu hija."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:106
translate spanish jamie14_9810dcb5:

    # pc "I'm glad she has a dad who loves her so much. I know she loves you very much too."
    pc "Me alegro de que tenga un padre que la quiera tanto. Sé que ella también te quiere mucho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:109
translate spanish jamie14_dde4aef6:

    # jd "Thanks, [pcname]. That makes me really glad to hear."
    jd "Gracias, [pcname]. Me alegra mucho oír eso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:110
translate spanish jamie14_884f0447:

    # jd "I hope she'll forgive me for all of this."
    jd "Espero que me perdone por todo esto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:111
translate spanish jamie14_961e07b1:

    # pc "I know she will."
    pc "Sé que lo hará."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:112
translate spanish jamie14_8a978913:

    # jd "My name is Richard, by the way. Rich to friends. I don't know if I've ever really introduced myself."
    jd "Por cierto, me llamo Richard. Rich para los amigos. No sé si alguna vez me he presentado de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:116
translate spanish jamie14_4c30d37e:

    # jd "Of course, I hadn't talked to you since you were a punk kid, playing Donkey Kong and sneaking feels in my daughter's bedroom."
    jd "Claro, no había hablado contigo desde que eras un crío rebelde, jugando al Donkey Kong y colándote a escondidas en la habitación de mi hija."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:117
translate spanish jamie14_078bc847:

    # pc "Oh we never did that."
    pc "Oh, nunca hicimos eso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:118
translate spanish jamie14_acfa9a92:

    # jd "Sure you didn't! And she was just sleeping over at your house last week because your bed is more comfortable."
    jd "¡Claro que no! Y ella se quedó a dormir en tu casa la semana pasada porque tu cama es más cómoda."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:119
translate spanish jamie14_e7874c6c:

    # pc "That's right."
    pc "Así es."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:120
translate spanish jamie14_f9b86ca6:

    # "He laughs and I find myself laughing with him. He's not so bad when he doesn't seem to want to kill me."
    "Él se ríe y yo me encuentro riéndome con él. No es tan malo cuando no parece querer matarme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:125
translate spanish jamie14_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_031.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_031.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:126
translate spanish jamie14_3b4e87c7:

    # gnd "Uh...What the heck is going on here?"
    gnd "Eh... ¿Qué diablos está pasando aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:127
translate spanish jamie14_7574532d:

    # jd "Oh, hey honey. I was about to go upstairs and get you. Dinner's ready."
    jd "Oh, hola, cariño. Iba a subir a buscarte. La cena está lista."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:128
translate spanish jamie14_23866c5e:

    # gnd "I am very confused right now. Why is [pcname] here?"
    gnd "Ahora mismo estoy muy confundida. ¿Por qué está [pcname] aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:131
translate spanish jamie14_e2bc8a1e:

    # jd "Because I made a mistake."
    jd "Porque cometí un error."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:132
translate spanish jamie14_0ed25bb5:

    # jd "In trying to protect you from getting your heart broken again..."
    jd "Al intentar protegerte para que no te rompieran el corazón otra vez..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:133
translate spanish jamie14_1d42c416:

    # jd "... I ended up breaking it myself."
    jd "... acabé rompiéndotelo yo mismo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:134
translate spanish jamie14_b2095d7e:

    # jd "I'm sorry honey."
    jd "Lo siento, cariño."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:135
translate spanish jamie14_f3239e98:

    # jd "I'm okay with you dating [pcname]. I'm okay with you doing whatever makes you happy."
    jd "No me importa que salgas con [pcname]. Me parece bien que hagas lo que te haga feliz."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:136
translate spanish jamie14_bb351aa3:

    # gnd "Really, Daddy?"
    gnd "¿De verdad, papá?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:137
translate spanish jamie14_ca7717c2:

    # jd "Really really."
    jd "De verdad, de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:140
translate spanish jamie14_4e39c56f:

    # gnd "Thank you, Daddy."
    gnd "Gracias, papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:141
translate spanish jamie14_04061eae:

    # jd "I love you, honey. I hope you know that."
    jd "Te quiero, cariño. Espero que lo sepas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:142
translate spanish jamie14_63418466:

    # gnd "I love you too, Daddy."
    gnd "Yo también te quiero, papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:143
translate spanish jamie14_0b8d1eb2:

    # jd "I'll take the steaks inside and get the table set. I know you two need to talk."
    jd "Llevaré los filetes dentro y pondré la mesa. Sé que vosotros dos tenéis que hablar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:146
translate spanish jamie14_69e44ecf:

    # "He carries the food inside and shuts the back door as Jamie walks slowly to me."
    "Lleva la comida dentro y cierra la puerta trasera mientras Jamie camina lentamente hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:148
translate spanish jamie14_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:149
translate spanish jamie14_24b3ee56:

    # gnd "I'm sorry that I cut things off like I did."
    gnd "Siento haber cortado las cosas como lo hice."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:150
translate spanish jamie14_4addc5b6:

    # gnd "I didn't know what to do."
    gnd "No sabía qué hacer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:151
translate spanish jamie14_607ff19c:

    # gnd "I've been crying about it all week."
    gnd "Llevo toda la semana llorando por eso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:153
translate spanish jamie14_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_032.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_032.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:154
translate spanish jamie14_83f69a35:

    # gnd "Are we okay?"
    gnd "¿Estamos bien?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:155
translate spanish jamie14_2e8693f0:

    # pc "Yeah, baby. We're okay."
    pc "Sí, cariño. Estamos bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:156
translate spanish jamie14_d481f95f:

    # pc "Come here."
    pc "Ven aquí."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:159
translate spanish jamie14_e043500c:

    # gnd "I missed you so much."
    gnd "Te he echado mucho de menos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:160
translate spanish jamie14_4295bf3d:

    # pc "I missed you too."
    pc "Yo también te he echado de menos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:161
translate spanish jamie14_c2110f18:

    # "We kiss like that for a long time. She clings to me like she never wants to let go."
    "Nos besamos así durante un buen rato. Ella se aferra a mí como si nunca quisiera soltarme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:164
translate spanish jamie14_d87fd08d:

    # "Then the back door opens and Rich peeks out."
    "Entonces se abre la puerta trasera y Rich asoma la cabeza."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:165
translate spanish jamie14_774c15a1:

    # jd "Oh, um... sorry. Honey, where is the A1?"
    jd "Oh, eh... lo siento. Cariño, ¿dónde está el A1?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:166
translate spanish jamie14_8d809a41:

    # "Jamie doesn't break off the kiss to answer, her lips never leaving mine."
    "Jamie no interrumpe el beso para responder, sus labios nunca se separan de los míos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:167
translate spanish jamie14_50d35669:

    # gnd "Bottom shelf of the refrigerator door."
    gnd "En el estante de abajo de la puerta de la nevera."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:168
translate spanish jamie14_13f55642:

    # jd "Okay, thanks honey."
    jd "Vale, gracias, cariño."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:169
translate spanish jamie14_d6a09f10:

    # jd "Um... everything's on the table, if you're ready to eat."
    jd "Eh... todo está en la mesa, si estáis listos para comer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:170
translate spanish jamie14_fc544f46:

    # gnd "Okay, Daddy. We'll be in in just a minute."
    gnd "Vale, papá. Estaremos ahí en un minuto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:171
translate spanish jamie14_232ae60e:

    # jd "Okay."
    jd "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:172
translate spanish jamie14_103466ed:

    # jd "Um... no rush."
    jd "Eh... no hay prisa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:173
translate spanish jamie14_f05f4276:

    # "He closes the door and goes back inside."
    "Cierra la puerta y vuelve a entrar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:176
translate spanish jamie14_22af107a:

    # gnd "You're right, you know. I should have just stood up and told him what was going on a long time ago."
    gnd "Tienes razón, ¿sabes? Debería haberme levantado y haberle dicho lo que pasaba hace mucho tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:177
translate spanish jamie14_16efaa2c:

    # pc "It all worked out in the end."
    pc "Al final todo salió bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:178
translate spanish jamie14_01c5d588:

    # gnd "Yeah, but... what if it hadn't."
    gnd "Sí, pero... ¿y si no hubiera sido así?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:179
translate spanish jamie14_e8c450c3:

    # gnd "I really need to work on that. Standing up for myself."
    gnd "De verdad tengo que trabajar en eso. Defenderme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:180
translate spanish jamie14_0821365b:

    # gnd "And I will."
    gnd "Y lo haré."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:182
translate spanish jamie14_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_033.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_033.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:183
translate spanish jamie14_58ddd8ce:

    # gnd "I'm making a promise. If I want something, I'm going to fight for it."
    gnd "Te lo prometo. Si quiero algo, voy a luchar por ello."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:185
translate spanish jamie14_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_034.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_034.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:186
translate spanish jamie14_e5bd6c1c:

    # gnd "I'm not going to let it slip away again, just because I might make somebody upset."
    gnd "No voy a dejar que se me escape otra vez, solo porque pueda molestar a alguien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:187
translate spanish jamie14_24f5981e:

    # pc "I like that. Your happiness is very important."
    pc "Me gusta eso. Tu felicidad es muy importante."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:190
translate spanish jamie14_1075fe75:

    # gnd "Well, I'm very happy right now."
    gnd "Bueno, ahora mismo estoy muy feliz."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:191
translate spanish jamie14_cee162e3:

    # gnd "Although if I knew you were coming, I would have dressed up a little. Maybe brushed my hair."
    gnd "Aunque si hubiera sabido que venías, me habría arreglado un poco. Quizás me habría peinado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:192
translate spanish jamie14_709e8dfa:

    # pc "You're gorgeous. Don't worry about that. I'm just glad to be here with you."
    pc "Estás preciosa. No te preocupes por eso. Simplemente me alegro de estar aquí contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:193
translate spanish jamie14_dfd62f7e:

    # gnd "You're so amazing."
    gnd "Eres increíble."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:194
translate spanish jamie14_c77df519:

    # gnd "Let's go eat."
    gnd "Vamos a comer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:198
translate spanish jamie14_1720c2ef:

    # "We go inside and sit with her dad and have dinner."
    "Entramos, nos sentamos con su padre y cenamos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:199
translate spanish jamie14_5d82c2b8:

    # "It's not as awkward as I was expecting it to be. Once he gets talking, Rich is pretty funny actually."
    "No es tan incómodo como esperaba. Una vez que empieza a hablar, Rich es bastante divertido, la verdad."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:200
translate spanish jamie14_9c723875:

    # "He talks about his work and asks about my school and work."
    "Habla de su trabajo y me pregunta por mis estudios y mi trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:201
translate spanish jamie14_bc6f8d22:

    # "He seems genuinely interested in me and over the course of the meal I can feel him warming up to me a bit."
    "Parece genuinamente interesado en mí y, a lo largo de la cena, noto que se va abriendo un poco conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:204
translate spanish jamie14_ea50946f:

    # jd "I was sorry to hear about your dad. Still no word on what happened to him?"
    jd "Siento lo de tu padre. ¿Aún no sabes qué le pasó?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:205
translate spanish jamie14_7fbf1a0e:

    # pc "No, not yet."
    pc "No, todavía no."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:206
translate spanish jamie14_487d47b7:

    # jd "It's really strange."
    jd "Es muy raro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:207
translate spanish jamie14_ede84000:

    # jd "We used to talk through the fence pretty often, but I hadn't seen him in months before the police got involved."
    jd "Solíamos hablar a través de la valla bastante a menudo, pero hacía meses que no lo veía antes de que se involucrara la policía."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:208
translate spanish jamie14_86681f0f:

    # pc "Yeah, he became a bit of a hermit, I guess. Spent all his time in his office in the basement."
    pc "Sí, se volvió un poco ermitaño, supongo. Se pasaba todo el tiempo en su despacho del sótano."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:211
translate spanish jamie14_913c87c9:

    # jd "Well, I hope he turns up."
    jd "Bueno, espero que aparezca."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:212
translate spanish jamie14_1bbf0a93:

    # jd "Hopefully he just took some time off to himself and he'll come home eventually."
    jd "Ojalá solo se haya tomado un tiempo para sí mismo y vuelva a casa tarde o temprano."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:213
translate spanish jamie14_e82b335f:

    # pc "I hope so."
    pc "Eso espero."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:214
translate spanish jamie14_4543d9f2:

    # "Sitting here and talking to Jamie's dad just reminds me how much I miss my own father."
    "Estar aquí sentada hablando con el padre de Jamie me recuerda lo mucho que echo de menos a mi propio padre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:217
translate spanish jamie14_09aa50f4:

    # "They are pretty similar actually. Hard-working. Funny."
    "En realidad, se parecen bastante. Son muy trabajadores. Divertidos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:218
translate spanish jamie14_fdfc1ad7:

    # "Both of them have lost their wife too."
    "Los dos han perdido a sus esposas también."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:219
translate spanish jamie14_c5b26d00:

    # "But while Jamie's dad turned to his family after the death and held them closer, my dad had..."
    "Pero mientras que el padre de Jamie se volcó en su familia tras la muerte y los unió más, mi padre tenía..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:220
translate spanish jamie14_1adb6623:

    # "... well, whatever my dad had done, I'm not really sure."
    "... bueno, lo que fuera que hiciera mi padre, no estoy muy segura."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:223
translate spanish jamie14_398e8474:

    # "After dinner, Jamie and I sit in her backyard together, looking up at the stars."
    "Después de cenar, Jamie y yo nos sentamos juntas en su jardín trasero, mirando las estrellas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:224
translate spanish jamie14_c08e5558:

    # gnd "That was really nice."
    gnd "Ha sido muy bonito."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:225
translate spanish jamie14_66c0b088:

    # pc "Yeah it was."
    pc "Sí, lo ha sido."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:226
translate spanish jamie14_73145f9f:

    # gnd "I love that we don't have to hide anymore."
    gnd "Me encanta que ya no tengamos que escondernos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:227
translate spanish jamie14_a8284af3:

    # pc "It's not going to ruin the passion?"
    pc "¿No va a arruinar la pasión?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:230
translate spanish jamie14_64527f8a:

    # gnd "Absolutely not."
    gnd "Por supuesto que no."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:231
translate spanish jamie14_37ba49d4:

    # gnd "I don't think Daddy is gonna want us having sex at the house or anything..."
    gnd "No creo que papá quiera que tengamos sexo en casa ni nada por el estilo..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:232
translate spanish jamie14_86cdae76:

    # gnd "... but I can't wait to spend another night with you."
    gnd "... pero estoy deseando pasar otra noche contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:233
translate spanish jamie14_04491fb2:

    # pc "Want to come over tonight?"
    pc "¿Quieres venir esta noche?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:236
translate spanish jamie14_5632c3e4:

    # gnd "Soon, but not tonight."
    gnd "Pronto, pero esta noche no."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:237
translate spanish jamie14_33db0ab9:

    # gnd "I think I need to talk to Daddy some alone, you know?"
    gnd "Creo que necesito hablar con papá a solas, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:238
translate spanish jamie14_9d09aa00:

    # gnd "It seems like we're better, but we still have some things we need to work through."
    gnd "Parece que estamos mejor, pero todavía hay algunas cosas que tenemos que resolver."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:239
translate spanish jamie14_34b44705:

    # pc "I understand."
    pc "Lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:242
translate spanish jamie14_8749741d:

    # gnd "But things are going to be good, I know it."
    gnd "Pero las cosas van a ir bien, lo sé."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:243
translate spanish jamie14_677d7bb7:

    # gnd "Thanks for everything, [pcname]."
    gnd "Gracias por todo, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:244
translate spanish jamie14_fe2167ed:

    # gnd "I know it probably wasn't easy to make tonight happen, to patch things up with Daddy."
    gnd "Sé que probablemente no fue fácil hacer que esto pasara esta noche, arreglar las cosas con papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:245
translate spanish jamie14_56e12139:

    # gnd "So thank you for doing that. For not holding things against him."
    gnd "Así que gracias por hacerlo. Por no guardarle rencor."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:248
translate spanish jamie14_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:249
translate spanish jamie14_f9831d1e:

    # gnd "I love you, [pcname]."
    gnd "Te quiero, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:250
translate spanish jamie14_5e3e613a:

    # pc "I love you too, Jamie."
    pc "Yo también te quiero, Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:251
translate spanish jamie14_53a4b911:

    # "We lie there for a while longer, holding each other and enjoying the cool night air."
    "Nos quedamos tumbados un rato más, abrazados y disfrutando del aire fresco de la noche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:254
translate spanish jamie14_f4805d30:

    # "Then I tell her and Rich goodbye and go back over to my house, leaving them to work out whatever they need to."
    "Luego me despido de ella y de Rich y vuelvo a mi casa, dejándolos a ellos para que resuelvan lo que tengan que resolver."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:255
translate spanish jamie14_acdbbb7b:

    # "It feels like Jamie and I took a big step in our relationship today."
    "Siento que Jamie y yo hemos dado hoy un gran paso en nuestra relación."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:256
translate spanish jamie14_9d2f13b4:

    # "Things are getting more serious. I promised her dad that I wouldn't hurt her."
    "Las cosas se están volviendo más serias. Le prometí a su padre que no le haría daño."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie14.rpy:257
translate spanish jamie14_ad87ea57:

    # "I hope I can keep that promise."
    "Espero poder cumplir esa promesa."

